OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOvernight mist and low cloud
OL,6,Fburning off this morning to leave a
OL,7,Fdry and mostly sunny day. Some
OL,8,Flingering cloud possible across the
OL,9,Feast. Warm in the sunshine, but cooler
OL,10,Falong the east coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FDry this evening with some
OL,13,Flate sunshine. Then the rest of the
OL,14,Fnight will be dry with mostly clear
OL,15,Fskies but some low cloud possible
OL,16,Facross the east. Patchy frost.
OL,17,
OL,18,CThursday:FDry and mostly sunny
OL,19,Falthough some patchy low cloud may
OL,20,Flinger along the North Sea coast.
OL,21,FWarm, but cooler along the east coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
